## Standard Header

```javascript
new Header({
  children: [
    new Paragraph({
      border: { bottom: { style: BorderStyle.SINGLE, size: 6, color: CS_ORANGE, space: 4 } },
      spacing: { after: 0 },
      children: [
        new TextRun({ text: "CENTRALSQUARE TECHNOLOGIES", font: "Arial", size: 16, bold: true, color: CS_DARK }),
        new TextRun({ text: "  |  ", font: "Arial", size: 16, color: CS_BORDER }),
        new TextRun({ text: "{{DOC_TYPE}} \u2014 CONFIDENTIAL", font: "Arial", size: 16, color: CS_ORANGE }),
      ]
    })
  ]
})
```

